summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Building Department; authorizing an agreement with King County, Washington providing for the administration of a grading permit by King County and a building permit by The City of Seattle in respect to the development of a certain tract of land lying partially within the City limits in the southwest quarter of the northwest quarter of Section 3, township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M. and partially in King County in the northwest quarter of the southwest quarter of Section 3, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M.
